      ** ¦ ===============                      ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
 
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Declared variables                   ¦
      ** ¦ ==================                   ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
 
      ** Average Rate Method passed as a parameter from calling program
     D  SAVRAM         S              1A
 
      ** Error message passed back to calling program from module
     D  Msgid1         S                   LIKE(#Msgid)
 
